Toxicroak (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0453: Croagunk
Pokémon
#0455: Carnivine →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Toxicroak (TCG Pocket).

Toxicroak has been featured on 18 different cards since it debuted in the Mysterious Treasures expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Toxicroak cards are normally Darkness-type or Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Toxicroak

Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
